{"type": "article", "id": 25308, "title": "空气净化器概念", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702113837ogbuzI97f6qJkAph.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个空气净化器的概念，是韩国室内设计师 Edgar Yeo 为韩国东洋美吉（TONGYANG MAGIC）设计的，目的是去除厨房里的油烟。净化器的轮廓的类似于戴森的无叶风扇，但它下面有一个扭曲的底座，灵感源于莫比乌斯带，配合内侧一圈霓虹效果的灯，增加了生活的绚丽。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113835m3UswhZS6c49JPRD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113836nCs3EWrbOzwp7Fgh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113836UQA4By1V6PXJqbzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113836qSdFJBf18IVu25Gs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}